433
00:30:33,289 --> 00:30:35,698
Ah, ya, ya, Dokter. Tolong jangan khawatir.

434
00:30:35,698 --> 00:30:39,069
Aku akan membawakan uangnya sebelum pukul 5 sore ini. Ya, baik.

435
00:30:54,019 --> 00:30:56,678
